类 ApplicationLauncher

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
main.ApplicationLauncher
public class ApplicationLauncher extends javafx.application.Application
JavaFX Application launcher class that extends Application. This class is responsible for starting the JavaFX application and displaying the login view.
从以下版本开始:
1.0

    • start

      public void start(javafx.stage.Stage primaryStage) throws Exception
      The main entry point for the JavaFX application. This method is called after the init method has returned, and after the system is ready for the application to begin running.
      指定者:
      start 在类中 javafx.application.Application
      参数:
      primaryStage - the primary stage for this application, onto which the application scene can be set
      抛出:
      Exception - if something goes wrong during application startup
